               <msContents class="#STM">
                  <summary><p>The <title xml:lang="ta">Civatarumōttiram</title>, also entitled <title xml:lang="ta">Civatarumōttirakāviyam</title> in the present manuscript, text with commentary, complete in 12 chapters, and followed by satellite stanzas (various <foreign xml:lang="sa">stuti</foreign>s, praises).</p>

<p>The bundle contains:
  <list rend="numbered">
    <item>An additional title page (U1).</item>
        <item>Invocation and preface (U2a + U2b).</item>
        <item>The text, complete in 12 chapters, and its commentary (U2c).</item>
        <item>A table of contents (U2c).</item></list></p>

<p>Description based on the examination of the original manuscript (April 2019).</p>
<p>Dimensions after Cabaton (1912).</p>      </summary>
                  
